w.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; width=&#34;400em&#34; height=&#34;1.28em&#34; viewbox=&#34;0 0 400000 1296&#34; preserveaspectratio=&#34;xMinYMin slice&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M263,681c0.7,0,18,39.7,52,119
